SIMPLE_SHELL 1 "2023-19-12" "Version 1.0" "Manuel de Simple Shell"
.hsh Simple Shell
simple_shell \- A light command interpretor writ in c language.

SYNOPSIS
simple_shell

## DESCRIPTION
The programm .hsh is a minimal command interpreter write in c language. it provides a command line interface for execut command system.

## OPTIONS
no options supported.

-----------------------------------------------------------

## Main controls

\cd
Change the work current directorie. if none directories specified, it moves to the user’s home directory.


\exit
Exit shell with the optionnel statut.


\help
Display a help command.

-----------------------------------------------------------

## UTILISATION

simple_shell

once shell start, you can entry a system command and push the entry button for execut.


ENVIRONNEMENT

\fIPATH\fR
Représente les répertoires où le shell recherche les exécutables.

.SH FICHIERS
.TP
\fI~/.simple_shellrc\fR
Le fichier de configuration du shell, exécuté à chaque lancement du shell.

